membrane by membrane.Visible stitching of membranes. Blue silk sewn to verso of opening. Three tagin on שעטנזגץ, and on בדהחק. A few majuscular or minuscular letters. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. Wooden roller with ivory elements (155mm high).
